game_instances.prompt:
You are shown the room you are currently in. This room is connected to other rooms. 
Your task is to explore all the rooms.
In each room you will be told in which cardinal direction you will be able to move.
Your answer needs to be in the following format: "MOVE: <direction>".
Replace <direction> by an appropriate cardinal direction ("north", "east", "south" or "west").
If you think you have seem all the rooms, answer "MOVE: stop" instead.
From your current room you can move in the following directions: [DIR]
